c: 9
v: 18
t: "Kuphela abahlala eMasjid kaMvelinqangi yilabo abakholwayo kuMvelinqangi nasosukwini lokugcina, benze imithandazo futhi bakhokhe izakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhwa kwabampofu) futhi bangesabi (omunye umuntu) ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi ngakho-ke kulindelekile ukuthi labo babengabaholiweyo"